2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of trainable transformations to improve the performance of neural networks. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of neural networks, which is a key area of research in AI. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is a possible category as the paper deals with improving the performance of neural networks, which is a key area of research in this field. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with image datasets and improving the performance of neural networks on these datasets.
